cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.CR, cs.PL 

This paper presents a learning-based approach to detecting failures in reactive systems, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The approach is based on active automata learning, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG). The technique is applied to IoT communication, which is a system (cs.SY) that involves communication protocols (cs.CR) and programming languages (cs.PL).
